If you prefer to be seen via video rather than in person, please select "Telehealth/Video Visit" as your primary reason when you reserve your spot.
Parents of infants less than 8 weeks old are recommended to seek care at the nearest Emergency Department.
Social distancing protocols are in place
We provide same-day care for infants older than 8 weeks, children and adults with non-life-threatening illnesses and injuries.
When you arrive at our clinic, a caregiver will check you in at the screening stations.
